{"tid":564626,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"2017年度最佳Linux版本出爐，Ubuntu奪冠 Linux Mint緊追在後","createTime":"2018-02-18T08:00:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T16:01:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40e2f9584c10e6587ad118d06192124d7a830bb1","tid":564626,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:00:08.000Z","msg":"年度桌面版Linux由Ubuntu獲取18.17％的票數獲勝，不過第二名的Linux Mint也有18.02％，而桌面版第三名的Slackware，以22.40％得票率獲得年度Linux伺服器版本第一名。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://s4.itho.me/sites/default/files/styles/picture_size_large/public/field/image/refine_fireshot_capture_111_-_linuxquestionsorg_-_-_https_wwwlinuxquestionsorg_questions_2017mcaphp.png?itok=5U0FWqup\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs4.itho.me%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fpicture_size_large%2Fpublic%2Ffield%2Fimage%2Frefine_fireshot_capture_111_-_linuxquestionsorg_-_-_https_wwwlinuxquestionsorg_questions_2017mcaphp.png%3Fitok%3D5U0FWqup&h=ee582721&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/121357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F121357&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=6c7afa92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ithome.com.tw/news/121357</a>"},{"pid":"20ab79bc7affda444d9087146bc2f467fc0707ec","tid":564626,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:00:28.000Z","msg":"擁有55萬會員，<a href=\"http://最大的Linux知識論壇LinuxQuestions.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E7%9A%84Linux%E7%9F%A5%E8%AD%98%E8%AB%96%E5%A3%87LinuxQuestions.org&d=gf5Gdp6S7239pWTH0YeD2ZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d2ab84a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">最大的Linux知識論壇LinuxQuestions.org</a>，日前對Linux使用者進行問卷調查，問題諸如最愛用的Linux版本，或是在Linux平臺最喜歡的開源遊戲等，並在2月公布了Linux使用者問卷調查的結果，約有1萬人參與問卷調查，年度最熱門Linux桌面版本出爐，由Ubuntu獲得18.17％使用者奪冠。"},{"pid":"bc8bd03c81be55365631a4fba3d9e398dc9da266","tid":564626,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"年度桌面版Linux由Ubuntu獲取18.17％的票數獲勝，不過第二名的Linux Mint也有18.02％，而桌面版第三名的Slackware，以22.40％得票率獲得年度Linux伺服器版本第一名，不過第二名與第三名的得票率也非常接近，分別是21.86％的CentOS，以及19.67％的Debian Stable。<br />\n<br />\n適合較舊硬體執行的輕量級Linux，其年度最佳版本為Puppy Linux得票率為29.75％，27.27％的antiX緊追在後。而桌面環境則由Plasma Desktop（KDE）27.83奪冠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，Xfce以微小差距23.55％位居第二，但第三名的Gnome Shell卻只有11.31％遠不及望其項背。"},{"pid":"3130a59807647f3180580fb4e1b123b8ed2fbe76","tid":564626,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:01:26.000Z","msg":"在應用程式方面，年度最佳瀏覽器仍然是Firefox，以超過一半以上的得票率57.84％得到第一名，其他瀏覽器包括Chrome在內都並非其對手，而年度影片媒體撥放器依然不意外的是VLC，年度最佳電子郵件軟體同樣也是由Mozilla Thunderbird奪冠。<br />\n<br />\nLinux使用者最愛的文字編輯器則依然是Vim，第二名的Nano得票率不到一半，不過頗有名氣的Emacs倒是還輸了第三名的Kate位居第四。年度最佳加密通訊軟體則有兩個，分別是Telegram與Signal。"},{"pid":"36982fed425a8ae8fd890319bd0da56223dd1916","tid":564626,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:01:41.000Z","msg":"這次的問卷有一個新類別，年度最佳視訊軟體由Microsoft Skype奪走，不少網友感到驚訝，LinuxQuestions創辦人Jeremy Garcia表示，新類別參與投票的人數極低，可能是產生這樣結果的原因。"},{"pid":"d10ec386a47cbd3a3dfea58495935278ade20a72","tid":564626,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/18/160227_c8c636d78d68a8209664df94bbcfe775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F18%2F160227_c8c636d78d68a8209664df94bbcfe775.jpg&h=27efcd49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n識貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！"},{"pid":"6bbabbfb636180ed4a70ba37474839f2845ca08a","tid":564626,"uid":61946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"兩年前都係睇用戶人數黎揀Ubuntu，然後用到